		SIF CFLAG:(FLAG:LOCALS):명중강화 < -16
			CFLAG:(FLAG:LOCALS):명중강화 = -16
		CFLAG:(FLAG:LOCALS):회피강화 -= 4
		SIF CFLAG:(FLAG:LOCALS):회피강화 < -16
